        "M124 230 q6 20 8 50 q2 30 -2 60 q-2 16 -8 24 q-4 2 -8 0 q-4 -16 -6 -36 q-4 -30 -4 -56 q0 -22 4 -38 q6 -8 16 -4 Z M118 320 q2 12 0 22 q-4 4 -8 2 q-2 -10 2 -22 q2 -4 6 -2 Z",
